songs.title: Interlude 2
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
You’re turned into W balls radio station
Always playing nothing but that hat
Seeing what’s happening big shout to Louisiana New Orleans Baton Rouge
(your attitude) and of course the Shreveport bay bay what’s happening
(is what describes you) matter of fact Cooking Soul let’s get into that YG
Why waste anymore time let’s go
